{
  "stem": "24242.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was the beginning of the partisans, if you will.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Woods.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the woods.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Under the sky, under trees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They would build, build a sort of, if you want to call it, a hut or a little room under the ground.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if there is a English word for that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, gets you out of the-- out of the cold.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's mainly for the winter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, it's-- you can lay down to sleep on it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a hole in the ground, but a big one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Enough for three, or four, or five people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that hole in the ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had blankets, whatever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We slept-- the second winter, the winter of 1942, they chased us out from one place of the woods into another.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, some way, somehow, it got-- we could never stay a long time in one place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to be constantly on the move.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It got to the Nazis where we at in the winter of 1942.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was in the height of the winter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it was in already in 1943, like January or February, because it was the height of the winter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And three weeks, we were sleeping on snow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah. 50, 60 people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who was in charge?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's hard to tell, exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] It was January.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know it was at the height of the winter of '42 that my brother, Tuvia, came to us in our area.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was for about six months, seven months under-- living under a Gentile name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was mixing with the Nazis, ate with them, with the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
